    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――八月三日　昼",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 133.33333329999996,
          "startTime": 0.9333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2800,
          "startTime": 3.6
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3633.3333333000005,
          "startTime": 4.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様ー。あ、千紗ちゃんもう着いてたんだ。今日の\nクイズ番組、頑張ろうね。『アイドル vs 弁護士』",
      "startTime": 8.1666667779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　渚ちゃんと琴乃ちゃんと一緒にお仕事するの\nめずらしいから、すっごく楽しみだったよ",
      "startTime": 17.2282457533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "それに、渚ちゃん今日お誕生日だよね。私、プレゼント\n用意してきたんだ。気に入ってくれるといいけど……",
      "startTime": 26.3000001113,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11133.333333300001,
          "startTime": 37.4333334446
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "ほんと！？　とっても嬉しいよ！\n千紗ちゃん、ありがとう！　なんだろう……？",
      "startTime": 34.4666656335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "わー！　海外TVドラマのブルーレイ！？\nしかも『ラブ＆グロテスク』の全巻セットだ！",
      "startTime": 42.8000001113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "私はホラーサイトで知ったんだけど\n内容的に渚ちゃんも観てるかなって思って",
      "startTime": 50.5000001113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん！　配信で観たんだけど、特典も付いてくるし\n買おうと思ってたもん。すぐにでも観たいくらいだよ",
      "startTime": 59.4000001113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "確かに怖いシーンもあるんだけど、やっぱり私は\nどろどろのスライムになった彼氏と主人公の恋愛かな",
      "startTime": 68.2666667779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "特に中盤で、主人公キャサリンが\nどろどろの彼氏とお風呂に入るシーン！",
      "startTime": 76.1822957372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "彼が湯船に溶けて見えなくなって……あそこは\n盛り上がったなぁ。ニヤニヤが止まらないよ～！",
      "startTime": 84.6333227635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "さすが渚ちゃん！　いいところ押さえてるね。私は\n恋敵の体に入ったどろどろの彼氏が飛び出すシーンかな",
      "startTime": 94.6000001113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "だってあの彼氏、鼻からいきなり飛び出すんだもん\nあれは7怖はいったよね～",
      "startTime": 103.8333334446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃんも分かってるね！　あのシーン\n正直びっくりしたけど、あれは本当の愛の形なんだよね",
      "startTime": 110.2999970596,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10600.0030517,
          "startTime": 120.9000001113
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、好きな作品の話って止まらないよ\nそれより千紗ちゃんってあっちもいける口なんだね",
      "startTime": 120.7666667779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "え、そ、そんなことないよ～私はまだまだ初心者だし\nそれより、渚ちゃんこそこっちに理解ある人なんだね",
      "startTime": 131.2666667779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "うん、でも嬉しいな。あっちもこっちも分かる人がいて\nそうだ、週末一緒に寮で観ようよ。琴乃ちゃんも誘って",
      "startTime": 141.4666637262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、楽しみだな、渚ちゃん、琴乃ちゃんとの鑑賞会\nじゃあ、そろそろこっちもあっちに行く？",
      "startTime": 152.8333303929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_53_02-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね、あっちでみんなこっちを待ってるしね\nこっちはこっちで\n『アイドル vs 弁護士』を楽しもう！",
      "startTime": 161.3666667779,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}